&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;By Month 6 (Full Ownership): &lt;/strong&gt;You will step into full customer ownership across your engagements, executing independently against a prioritized backlog managed by your partner Engagement Manager (EM). You will build and deploy production-grade solutions across the entire MLOps lifecycle (development, deployment, and monitoring) while actively advising data science teams on Domino best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
